commit.message:
Release HOWTO: save to Web Archive after each update

VPS provider that hosts newsboat.org had a multi-day outage, and for
some time there was risk that all data is lost. Web Archive had an
*almost* complete copy of the site though. Let's make sure that it's
always complete in the future.

Add xslt transformation for replacing Slashdot's newlines

Had some trouble getting the `replace()` call to work.
Finally found a solution at https://stackoverflow.com/questions/3067113/xslt-string-replace/59815107#59815107
However, a comment below it mentions that it is (or was) not available
on the macOS 10.13 version of xsltproc.
